# CSLKit

A Swift library for interacting with the Cardano Serialization Library (CSL) in iOS applications.

## Overview

CSLKit provides a Swift interface to the Cardano Serialization Library, enabling iOS applications to work with Cardano blockchain data structures and operations. 
The library handles the complex interactions between Swift and the underlying Rust implementation, providing a clean and type-safe API.

## Features

- Type-safe wrappers for Cardano data structures
- Automatic memory management for Rust pointers
- Comprehensive error handling
- Support for common Cardano operations:
  - Address handling
  - Asset management
  - Transaction building
  - Certificate processing
  - And more...

